{
  "stem": "2097.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And everything will be very fine, because they loved the Hungarians.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes. many, many Jews-- they were very happy that the Hungarian came.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From the past.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From the past, because they were very happy during the Austro-Hungarian empire.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- but the-- the-- as soon they arrived, the-- the pressure, anyway, was in Europe before.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The pressure was harder.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they took away the license from the Jews.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They had stores, little stores.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Or they went to the market.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There were markets where they're selling little merchandises.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They took away the licenses.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They couldn't sell, anymore.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And it was very, very far.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And that, in this time, when the Hungarian occupied, my mother and my father, they were in the hospital in Oradea.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And first time that my father heard that the Hungarian-- now is Hungary, he was upset that he thought, why he is in Hungary, because his children are in Romania?",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I don't know how long I could talk, so I'd like to make it-- No, please.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I could talk.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because if I--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, it is, OK.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And finally, in the end of the year-- about in December-- I supposed to go to school.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But in Marghita, there was no Jewish school.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I couldn't go to school.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And finally, in the end of December, we went home-- the whole family-- to Simleu.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then I went back to the school, which was Jewish school.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it was already organized for the-- for my age children, to get a formal education in Hungarian-- in Hungarian, by Jewish professors, which was both from Miskolc and other Hungarian cities.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we were-- we were just studying and growing every day.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the-- the pressure was constantly, and the-- the very hard time, we had-- everybody.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We had to eat.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
